title: Further refactoring
message:

inbuilt one to reduce battery demands

or snippet (mainly to prevent it appearing when tapping the 'My
Location' marker)

title: Fix map display on slower devices
message:
Fix map display on slower devices

On slower devices we might reach onMapLoaded() before the default bounds
have been initialised which will cause animateCamera to fail.

Work around this by performing initial animation only when default
bounds are ready, which may be in onMapLoaded or onPostExecute().
